        "## 3. TDD en Acción: Ejemplo Completo\n",
        "\n",
        "### Problema: Calculadora de Descuentos\n",
        "\n",
        "Vamos a implementar una calculadora de descuentos usando TDD. Queremos una función que calcule el precio final después de aplicar descuentos por volumen:\n",
        "- 0-9 items: sin descuento\n",
        "- 10-49 items: 10% descuento\n",
        "- 50+ items: 20% descuento\n",
        "\n",
        "### Iteración 1: Caso más simple\n",
        "\n",
        "**RED: Escribe el test**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "import pytest\n",
        "\n",
        "# RED: Test fails because function doesn't exist\n",
        "def test_calculate_price_no_discount():\n",
        "    \"\"\"Test price calculation with no volume discount.\"\"\"\n",
        "    result = calculate_bulk_price(unit_price=10.0, quantity=5)\n",
        "    assert result == 50.0\n",
        "\n",
        "# Running this test would fail with: NameError: name 'calculate_bulk_price' is not defined"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**GREEN: Implementación más simple**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# GREEN: Simplest code to make test pass\n",
        "def calculate_bulk_price(unit_price: float, quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate total price with volume discounts.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param unit_price: Price per unit\n",
        "    :type unit_price: float\n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Total price after discount\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    return unit_price * quantity\n",
        "\n",
        "# Test now passes!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**REFACTOR: No hay nada que refactorizar todavía**\n",
        "\n",
        "El código es simple y claro. Pasamos a la siguiente iteración.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Iteración 2: Descuento del 10%\n",
        "\n",
        "**RED: Nuevo test para descuento**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# RED: Test for 10% discount (10-49 items)\n",
        "def test_calculate_price_10_percent_discount():\n",
        "    \"\"\"Test price calculation with 10% volume discount.\"\"\"\n",
        "    result = calculate_bulk_price(unit_price=10.0, quantity=10)\n",
        "    assert result == 90.0  # 100 - 10% = 90\n",
        "\n",
        "# This test fails: expected 90.0, got 100.0"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**GREEN: Añade lógica de descuento**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# GREEN: Add discount logic\n",
        "def calculate_bulk_price(unit_price: float, quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate total price with volume discounts.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param unit_price: Price per unit\n",
        "    :type unit_price: float\n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Total price after discount\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    total = unit_price * quantity\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if quantity >= 10:\n",
        "        total = total * 0.9  # 10% discount\n",
        "    \n",
        "    return total\n",
        "\n",
        "# Both tests now pass!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**REFACTOR: Mejora la claridad**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# REFACTOR: Extract magic numbers to constants\n",
        "TIER_1_THRESHOLD = 10\n",
        "TIER_1_DISCOUNT = 0.10\n",
        "\n",
        "def calculate_bulk_price(unit_price: float, quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate total price with volume discounts.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param unit_price: Price per unit\n",
        "    :type unit_price: float\n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Total price after discount\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    total = unit_price * quantity\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if quantity >= TIER_1_THRESHOLD:\n",
        "        total = total * (1 - TIER_1_DISCOUNT)\n",
        "    \n",
        "    return total\n",
        "\n",
        "# Tests still pass after refactoring!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Iteración 3: Descuento del 20%\n",
        "\n",
        "**RED: Test para descuento mayor**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# RED: Test for 20% discount (50+ items)\n",
        "def test_calculate_price_20_percent_discount():\n",
        "    \"\"\"Test price calculation with 20% volume discount.\"\"\"\n",
        "    result = calculate_bulk_price(unit_price=10.0, quantity=50)\n",
        "    assert result == 400.0  # 500 - 20% = 400\n",
        "\n",
        "# This test fails: expected 400.0, got 450.0 (only 10% discount applied)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**GREEN: Añade segundo nivel de descuento**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# GREEN: Add second discount tier\n",
        "TIER_1_THRESHOLD = 10\n",
        "TIER_1_DISCOUNT = 0.10\n",
        "TIER_2_THRESHOLD = 50\n",
        "TIER_2_DISCOUNT = 0.20\n",
        "\n",
        "def calculate_bulk_price(unit_price: float, quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate total price with volume discounts.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param unit_price: Price per unit\n",
        "    :type unit_price: float\n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Total price after discount\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    total = unit_price * quantity\n",
        "    \n",
        "    if quantity >= TIER_2_THRESHOLD:\n",
        "        total = total * (1 - TIER_2_DISCOUNT)\n",
        "    elif quantity >= TIER_1_THRESHOLD:\n",
        "        total = total * (1 - TIER_1_DISCOUNT)\n",
        "    \n",
        "    return total\n",
        "\n",
        "# All three tests now pass!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "**REFACTOR: Función auxiliar para calcular descuento**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# REFACTOR: Extract discount calculation\n",
        "TIER_1_THRESHOLD = 10\n",
        "TIER_1_DISCOUNT = 0.10\n",
        "TIER_2_THRESHOLD = 50\n",
        "TIER_2_DISCOUNT = 0.20\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_discount_rate(quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Get discount rate based on quantity.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Discount rate (0.0 to 1.0)\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    if quantity >= TIER_2_THRESHOLD:\n",
        "        return TIER_2_DISCOUNT\n",
        "    elif quantity >= TIER_1_THRESHOLD:\n",
        "        return TIER_1_DISCOUNT\n",
        "    return 0.0\n",
        "\n",
        "def calculate_bulk_price(unit_price: float, quantity: int) -> float:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Calculate total price with volume discounts.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param unit_price: Price per unit\n",
        "    :type unit_price: float\n",
        "    :param quantity: Number of items\n",
        "    :type quantity: int\n",
        "    :return: Total price after discount\n",
        "    :rtype: float\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    total = unit_price * quantity\n",
        "    discount_rate = get_discount_rate(quantity)\n",
        "    return total * (1 - discount_rate)\n",
        "\n",
        "# All tests still pass, code is cleaner!"
      ]
    },
