      "source": [
        "## 6. TDD vs Testing Tradicional\n",
        "\n",
        "### Comparación de Enfoques\n",
        "\n",
        "**Testing Tradicional (Test-Last):**\n",
        "```\n",
        "1. Escribir código de producción\n",
        "2. Probar manualmente\n",
        "3. Escribir tests automatizados (tal vez)\n",
        "4. Encontrar bugs en producción\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "**Test-Driven Development (Test-First):**\n",
        "```\n",
        "1. Escribir test que falla\n",
        "2. Escribir código mínimo para pasar\n",
        "3. Refactorizar\n",
        "4. Repetir\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n",
        "### Diferencias Clave\n",
        "\n",
        "| Aspecto | Test-Last | Test-First (TDD) |\n",
        "|---------|-----------|------------------|\n",
        "| **Diseño** | Código dicta tests | Tests dictan código |\n",
        "| **Cobertura** | Variable, a menudo baja | Alta, por diseño |\n",
        "| **Refactoring** | Arriesgado | Seguro |\n",
        "| **Debugging** | Más tiempo | Menos tiempo |\n",
        "| **Documentación** | Separada del código | Tests son documentación |\n",
        "| **Confianza** | Baja | Alta |\n",
        "\n",
        "### Ejemplo Comparativo\n",
        "\n",
        "**Enfoque Test-Last:**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# BAD: Test-Last approach\n",
        "# 1. Write implementation first\n",
        "def validate_password(password: str) -> bool:\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    Validate password strength.\n",
        "    \n",
        "    :param password: Password to validate\n",
        "    :type password: str\n",
        "    :return: True if valid\n",
        "    :rtype: bool\n",
        "    \"\"\"\n",
        "    # Implementation written without thinking about edge cases\n",
